<html><body><div class="dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden" style="display: none;"><img width="512" height="1024" decoding="async" src="https://thenaturalnurturer.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/3-512x1024.png" data-pin-media="https://thenaturalnurturer.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/3.png" data-pin-title="Instant Pot Artichokes" data-pin-description="Have you ever made Instant Pot Artichokes? It is my favorite way to make this delicious vegetable and cooking artichoke in your pressure cooker is easy! #healthyinstantpot #instantpotrecipes #instantpotvegetables #thenaturalnurturer #veggieloaded" class="skip-lazy a3-notlazy no-lazyload dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-inner  dpsp-post-pinterest-image-hidden-single" data-no-lazy="1"></div><span id="dpsp-post-content-markup" data-image-pin-it="true"></span>
<p class="has-medium-font-size">Cooking fresh artichokes perfectly in an Instant Pot couldn&rsquo;t be easier. This simple and quick recipe is my favorite way to cook this vegetable. Guidance for cutting and prepping fresh artichokes for the Instant Pot included!</p>
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="698" height="1050" data-pin-description="Have you ever made Instant Pot Artichokes? It is my favorite way to make this delicious vegetable and cooking artichoke in your pressure cooker is easy and quick! " src="https://thenaturalnurturer.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/instant-pot-artichoke-1-of-3.jpg" alt="Two artichokes in an Instant Pot, upside down, before cooking. " class="wp-image-12567" srcset="https://thenaturalnurturer.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/instant-pot-artichoke-1-of-3.jpg 698w, https://thenaturalnurturer.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/instant-pot-artichoke-1-of-3-360x542.jpg 360w, https://thenaturalnurturer.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/instant-pot-artichoke-1-of-3-150x226.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 698px) 100vw, 698px" data-pin-media="https://thenaturalnurturer.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/instant-pot-artichoke-1-of-3.jpg" data-skip-lazy="1"></figure>
<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-instant-pot-artichokes">Instant Pot Artichokes</h2>
<p class="has-medium-font-size"> Artichokes are one of those veggies that I am still teaching myself to buy, make and enjoy, TNNers. While I enjoy their flavor and find them fun to eat, I have always found artichokes to be a &ldquo;fussy&rdquo; vegetable that seemed to be a pain to cook. </p>
<p class="has-medium-font-size">However, my daughter recently has become obsessed with the idea of artichokes and so I banking on that veggie interest of her&rsquo;s and looking for easy ways to get artichokes on the menu more often!</p>
<p class="has-medium-font-size">And you know what I have discovered? Artichokes in the Instant Pot are the least fussy, time consuming way to make these veggies! </p>
<p class="has-medium-font-size">You know that I love <strong><a href="https://thenaturalnurturer.com/category/cooking-methods/instant-pot/">easy Instant pot recipes</a></strong>, so while I was totally dazzled to find out that cooking artichokes in the Instant Pot is a game changer! Done in about 30 minutes and super easy to make, this healthy how-to is the perfect fast way to add vegetables to the table, even on a busy night!</p>
