<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-to-select-an-artichoke">How to select an artichoke</h2>
<ul class="has-medium-font-size wp-block-list">
<li><strong><em>Buy artichokes with closed petals.</em></strong> This is a sign that they are fresher and will be much more tender to eat! </li>
<li><strong>Opt for artichokes that feel a bit heavy</strong>. You can do this by holding different artichokes in each hand and comparing their weight. The lighter artichokes are more likely to be drier and produce less meat after cooking in your Instant Pot. </li>
<li><strong><em>The greener the better.</em></strong> This is a sign that they are nice and fresh. Wilted and dry artichokes will taste blah.</li>
</ul>
